[ Engine shuts off ]

24:29.210 --> 24:32.611
[ Man shouts in distance,
crow caws ]

24:38.710 --> 24:39.699
You Petey?

24:39.710 --> 24:40.825
Who's asking?

24:43.210 --> 24:46.782
This man been to see you
in the last 24 hours?

24:48.790 --> 24:51.111
