I'll go with you.

25:42.670 --> 25:44.035
You know...

25:44.040 --> 25:45.667
I'll hold on to your phone.

25:45.670 --> 25:47.706
Wouldn't want you
dropping it in the toilet.

25:47.710 --> 25:49.246
I won't drop it.

25:49.250 --> 25:53.038
I'll take it anyway,
just in case.

25:53.040 --> 25:56.498
