25:56.500 --> 25:58.821
Even though...

25:58.830 --> 26:00.786
Hey, kid, that's...

26:00.790 --> 26:02.280
the ladies'.

26:03.790 --> 26:06.247
[ Toilet flushes ]

26:06.250 --> 26:09.287
[ Music continues, muffled ]

26:09.290 --> 26:10.746
[ Stall door opens ]

26:10.750 --> 26:12.069
[ Chuckling ] Oh.

26:12.080 --> 26:13.490
