tear my heart apart

26:24.500 --> 26:25.740
Oops.

26:25.750 --> 26:28.321
Yeah, yeah, yeah

26:28.330 --> 26:30.412
So, hey, babe, won't you...

26:34.710 --> 26:37.998
[ Sighs ]

26:38.000 --> 26:41.117
[ Siren walls in distance ]

26:57.830 --> 27:00.162
[ Cellphone vibrates, rings ]

27:00.170 --> 27:02.616
[ Drawer closes ]

27:02.620 --> 27:04.497
Hello?

27:04.500 --> 27:06.320
Waitress: I need to talk
to Dex ParIos.

27:06.330 --> 27:07.570
Yeah. This is she.

27:07.580 --> 27:10.162
A young man gave me a card,
and it says,

27:10.170 --> 27:12.661
"My name is Ansel Parios.
Please call my sister.

27:12.670 --> 27:14.240
Tell her I'm lost
and to come get me."

27:14.250 --> 27:15.615
It had this number.

27:15.620 --> 27:16.996
Where is he?

27:17.000 --> 27:19.241
Uh, Pearl's Diner on
