what does he look like?

27:23.420 --> 27:25.376
I don't know.
Middle-aged, bald.

27:26.880 --> 27:28.029
Uh, gray jacket?

27:28.040 --> 27:28.916
Yeah, that's him.

27:28.920 --> 27:30.319
Okay.
I'll be right there.

27:34.750 --> 27:37.617
[The Cars'
"Just What I Needed" plays ]

27:44.040 --> 27:45.951
[ Brakes screech lightly ]

27:45.960 --> 27:48.110
[ Gearshift clicks,
cellphone beeps ]

27:48.120 --> 27:49.701
[ Ringing ]
Hoffman.

27:49.710 --> 27:51.917
Yeah, Hoffman, Pearl's Diner.
Make it quick, okay?

27:51.920 --> 27:53.069
[ Cellphone beeps ]

27:54.460 --> 27:55.666
This is
the employee entrance.

27:55.670 --> 27:56.910
Okay. What's your name?
Henry.

27:56.920 --> 27:58.660
Henry. Okay.
Won't happen again.

28:00.670 --> 28:01.876
Uh, hey.

28:01.880 --> 28:03.029
