28:30.670 --> 28:31.739
Yeah. Got it.

28:31.750 --> 28:32.785
Okay.
I'll tell you what.

28:32.790 --> 28:34.280
Why don't you wait for me
in the car?

28:34.290 --> 28:35.746
It's in the parking lot,
okay?

28:35.750 --> 28:38.571
Frank and I are just gonna have
a little...talk.

28:38.580 --> 28:40.207
What about
the cilantro?

28:40.210 --> 28:41.495
Don't worry about
the cilantro.

28:44.080 --> 28:46.116
I can stay with you.

28:46.120 --> 28:48.532
No.
Uh, I got it, okay?

28:48.540 --> 28:50.610
Just go wait in the car.

28:50.620 --> 28:52.281
Is Grey okay?

28:52.290 --> 28:53.666
Grey is fine.
I promise.

28:53.670 --> 28:54.955
I'll be out in a minute,
alright?

28:54.960 --> 28:56.325
Okay.
Okay.

28:56.330 --> 28:58.537
I love you.
I love you, too, buddy.

28:58.540 --> 29:00.030
[ Chuckles ]

29:02.830 --> 29:04.957
Just keep your hands
on the table, okay?

29:06.210 --> 29:08.201
Where's Grey?
I have no idea.

29:08.210 --> 29:09.780
Well, you better tell me
where he is,

29:09.790 --> 29:11.246
or there's gonna be
a little trouble downtown.

29:13.920 --> 29:16.286
He's with Kane,
settling a debt.

29:16.290 --> 29:18.076
I was supposed to hold on
to you for insurance,

29:18.080 --> 29:19.820
but the kid was
the next best thing.

29:19.830 --> 29:20.956
Waitress:
Everything good here?

29:20.960 --> 29:23.281
Yeah. It's wonderful.
Thank you.

29:23.290 --> 29:24.826
Are you the person
I called on the phone?

29:24.830 --> 29:26.377
I sure am, yeah.

29:26.380 --> 29:27.950
And everything
is, uh, hunlq-dory.

29:27.960 --> 29:29.109
[ Chuckles ]

29:30.420 --> 29:31.705
[ Table thuds ]

29:31.710 --> 29:32.495
[ Gun cocks ]

29:32.500 --> 29:34.036
Alright.

29:34.040 --> 29:36.782
We're walking out of here
through the back.

29:36.790 --> 29:38.371
We're gonna get
into your car,

29:38.380 --> 29:40.701
and you and the kid
are coming with me.

29:40.710 --> 29:41.995
Whatever you say, okay?

29:42.000 --> 29:43.035
After you.

29:43.040 --> 29:46.783
I don't mind you comin' here

29:46.790 --> 29:48.667
And wastin' all my time

29:50.540 --> 29:53.782
'Cause when you're standin'
oh so near

29:53.790 --> 29:54.916
Keep walking.

29:54.920 --> 29:56.319
I kinda lose my mind

29:56.330 --> 29:57.661
Ha!

29:57.670 --> 29:58.910
[ Both grunting ]

29:58.920 --> 30:02.412
It's not the perfume
that you wear

30:02.420 --> 30:04.615
It's _not the ribbons
In your haIr

30:04.620 --> 30:06.030
[ Gun clatters ]

30:06.040 --> 30:09.828
And I don't mind
you comIn' here

30:09.830 --> 30:12.071
And wastin' all my time

30:14.000 --> 30:15.786
I guess you're just
what I needed

30:15.790 --> 30:16.529
Just what I needed

30:16.540 --> 30:17.825
Aaah!

30:17.830 --> 30:20.162
