[ Speaking indistinctly]

37:49.830 --> 37:52.742
Yes, I'm -- I'm thrilled
that you're happy.

37:52.750 --> 37:54.536
Have a good evening.

37:54.540 --> 37:56.076
You too.

37:58.170 --> 37:59.114
The mayor.

37:59.120 --> 38:00.951
And the chief.

38:00.960 --> 38:02.871
You are moving up
in this world, Hoffman.

38:02.880 --> 38:04.370
[ Liquid sloshes ]

38:04.380 --> 38:05.995
What about McConnell?

38:06.000 --> 38:07.160
[ Bottle thuds ]

38:07.170 --> 38:09.411
Um, what --
what about him?

38:09.420 --> 38:10.990
What are we gonna
charge him with?

38:12.710 --> 38:14.416
Um...nothing.

38:14.420 --> 38:16.160
[ Liquid pours ]

38:16.170 --> 38:18.320
Uh, he was, um --
[ Bottle thuds ]

38:18.330 --> 38:20.161
[ Clears throat ]
He -- He was --

38:20.170 --> 38:22.070
He was my informant.

38:22.080 --> 38:25.993
And he was, um, integral
to [Clears throat]

38:26.000 --> 38:27.570
the -- the whole takedown.

38:28.960 --> 38:30.075
Is that right?

38:30.080 --> 38:31.490
Y-Yeah.

38:31.500 --> 38:32.615
He was a C.I.?

38:34.080 --> 38:36.071
And I didn't see any paperwork
cross my desk.

38:36.080 --> 38:37.411
Yeah.

38:37.420 --> 38:41.618
